description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 40, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 40, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Stringalong for East, 5 for South, and 5 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30401-37551-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [40 Votes, Common]
